OL,3,CWoman with MS on fight for disabled
OL,4,Cpeople to have carers in hospital
OL,6,FShe is calling for Nina's Law - where
OL,7,Fall hospitals across the country would
OL,8,Fhave to allow carers to continue to
OL,9,Fhelp their patients alongside hospital
OL,10,Fstaff.
OL,12,F"It would change lives," she said.
OL,13,F"People would not be frightened about
OL,14,Fgoing into hospital and saying things
OL,15,Flike, I'd rather die at home with my
OL,16,Ffamily and carers. I want to give
OL,17,Fthose in need a voice, this really
OL,18,Fdoes need to happen."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
