OL,3,CWoman with MS on fight for disabled
OL,4,Cpeople to have carers in hospital
OL,6,FIn just a few weeks Nina's petition
OL,7,Fhas collected more than 20,000
OL,8,Fsignatures and she has the backing
OL,9,Ffrom her local MP.
OL,11,FWill Stone, The Labour MP for Swindon
OL,12,FNorth said: "I can't see a reason not
OL,13,Fto support this. Firstly, it can
OL,14,Freduce the burden and stress on the
OL,15,Fnurses. Secondly we have patients with
OL,16,Fcomplex needs and if we can have a
OL,17,Fcarer who already understands them,
OL,18,Fthat can make a massive difference in
OL,19,Fsupporting them and making them feel
OL,20,Fcomfortable."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
